{"tid":2122314,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）兩年一度既盛事，aco狗衝比賽受注了!","createTime":"2020-07-24T02:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T12:58:33.000Z","uid":102456,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e14214e04511c4115a716d70dc6493bf160d448d","tid":2122314,"uid":102456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"ACO---公務員界入面既筍工又開始招聘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上而家咁既時勢，一撚定大把人申請入正苦做，今年既競爭一定會大好很多<br />\n<br />\n要係眾多競爭對手之中脫穎而出，你需要既係集思廣益，同一眾巴絲打一齊研究致勝之道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好誤會，呢個唔係hard sell post，不過click入下面條link就會搵到同路人圍爐取暖，你唔係仲唔嚟呀嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想識朋友仔既都可以入嚟吹下水，亦都歡迎現職公墓園同事入嚟交流下辦公心得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----------完-----------<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EB9m9RgeMhEMtyvKi6SAFw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEB9m9RgeMhEMtyvKi6SAFw&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6P1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=1d880a6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EB9m9RgeMhEMtyvKi6SAFw</a>"},{"pid":"ab98fa80e8a0e8f4b051d8a50489e2b40101e43e","tid":2122314,"uid":231640,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:36:12.000Z","msg":"你地班兒登仔 做左aco 無得去英國呀 屌你"},{"pid":"e79c08e4f78053cd188097a0d6aaabe017cd9b30","tid":2122314,"uid":102456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab98fa80e8a0e8f4b051d8a50489e2b40101e43e","tid":2122314,"uid":231640,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:36:12.000Z","msg":"你地班兒登仔 做左aco 無得去英國呀 屌你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:43:01.000Z","msg":"相信黨，沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62cd2fb3c4e3dc4d185701c3d303c4d759ef5eb4","tid":2122314,"uid":102456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:44:29.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd978f22bacc150eed0fa714a29bf03a8ff098b","tid":2122314,"uid":102456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:48:22.000Z","msg":"推到所有準考生入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd5bfce0f5521b1a35cbf367a7d917fc70699c0","tid":2122314,"uid":4213,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:52:07.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n做十三年就有30K<br />\n你班人諗下<br />\n你地讀埋啲垃圾Asso/ HD/ LU BU之流既垃圾degree<br />\n做十五年都未必有30K<br />\n而家做ACO呢啲智障都識做既工 日日準時收工<br />\n十五年後就可以做大帝<br />\n唔係唔做啊嘛?<br />\n<br />\n實有人話 屌你老母<br />\n30K 都高? 高你老母咩<br />\n係人都知30K唔高啦<br />\n但個重點係<br />\n你地班垃圾要知道自己係垃圾<br />\n你班垃圾如果連現實都唔肯接受的話<br />\n莫講話30K<br />\n25K都唔會有得你班垃圾拎<br />\n<br />\n所以我勸各位垃圾早日接受現實<br />\n快快手做ACO 早起步 廿年後可能升埋你做CO呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f16968689970e995070f349df425b88ae091c76","tid":2122314,"uid":109923,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:53:50.000Z","msg":"事實係ACO跑輸好多大學生，建議有degree唔好狗衝<br />\n<br />\n利 做緊ACO，跑輸身邊所有大學同學"},{"pid":"eab537199d958a234bdb85dc43982e99d5990b98","tid":2122314,"uid":151196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:55:06.000Z","msg":"做緊ACO<br />\n跑輸身邊所有IVE 同學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7da1c0c96ce16169051aeaf16d2a087a4e309ca","tid":2122314,"uid":102456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:56:13.000Z","msg":"一推再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50132ca4429b2dfb0df036b9b7a1de314b63f065","tid":2122314,"uid":102456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:00:25.000Z","msg":"筍工上架啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f1b97ae522a17728cece3d855bd30453399e5f","tid":2122314,"uid":102456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:03:22.000Z","msg":"逆市筍工，好過做啦港姐啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7f00e21ffd5cebda255b8dd945f3ed19150520","tid":2122314,"uid":362459,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:07:56.000Z","msg":"應該只有垃圾會想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:準備做垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435bd709032148b95407481e841bebfe07d93129","tid":2122314,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c7f00e21ffd5cebda255b8dd945f3ed19150520","tid":2122314,"uid":362459,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:07:56.000Z","msg":"應該只有垃圾會想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:準備做垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"欣賞<br />\n社會係必需要有低下階層先可以運作到<br />\n但低下階層都有分tier<br />\n你提早接受現實 就會有更大機會升到去低下階層入面既較高tier<br />\n以ACO來講 就係更大機會升做CO SCO<br />\n快快手去報啦 係ACO界 一年差距已經好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c081b347ad8c9788cacd1f2920d1e960dc9df641","tid":2122314,"uid":102456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:26:12.000Z","msg":"I say one two three four<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613817ea5f70149086d8f67a82191bf4d78f8671","tid":2122314,"uid":362459,"l